Subject: [PATCH] Beta prep: LICENSE, README, E2E fixes for public release
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Add MIT LICENSE at repo root (PARK Systems Corporation 2026)
- Add top-level README with quick start and feature overview
- Fix unused/duplicate imports in terminal and connection-manager modules
- Replace hardcoded LLM_SERVER_URL with relative URL (nginx-proxied)
- Fix unsafe `as any` type assertion in completion contribution
- Add __pycache__ to .gitignore
- Add nginx/ssl/.gitkeep placeholder for HTTPS cert deployment
- All extensions, Python server, Docker stack, nginx, and shell scripts
  pass E2E validation — ready for beta testing

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
